}

let name = Some("Alice")
let email = Some("alice@example.com")
let age = Some(30)

let user = option.map3(name, email, age, User)
// user == Some(User("Alice", "alice@example.com", 30))
```

Si alguno de los tres Option es None, el resultado será None:

```aiken
