`has_any_nft_strict` encapsulates all of the following in one call:
- The value contains exactly one non-Ada policy (the target policy).
- That policy has exactly one asset name.
- That asset has quantity 1 (i.e., it is an NFT).
- No other non-Ada tokens are present.

