Use `assets.merge/2` to combine two `Value` objects. It takes a left and right `Value` and returns their combination:

```aiken
use cardano/assets

let value_a = assets.from_lovelace(2_000_000)
let value_b = assets.from_asset("abcd1234", "MyToken", 10)
let combined = assets.merge(value_a, value_b)
