`validate_withdraw_with_amount` checks:
1. That the redeemer at index 0 has a `Withdraw(Script(withdraw_script_hash))` purpose.
2. That the withdrawal at index 0 belongs to the same `Script(withdraw_script_hash)` credential.
3. Calls your lambda with the redeemer and the withdrawn Lovelace amount — here asserting `amount > 0`.

```aiken
use aiken/crypto.{ScriptHash}
use aiken_design_patterns/stake_validator
use cardano/transaction.{OutputReference, Transaction}

