`self.extra_signatories` is the verified field on `Transaction` that holds the list of required signers. Never call a non-existent `transaction.signatories(tx)` function — access the field directly.

Usa `interval.is_entirely_before` sobre `self.validity_range` para confirmar que toda la ventana de validez cae antes del slot límite:

```aiken
use aiken/interval
use cardano/transaction.{Transaction, OutputReference}

validator deadline_check {
  spend(
    _datum: Option<Void>,
    _redeemer: Void,
    _own_ref: OutputReference,
    self: Transaction,
  ) -> Bool {
    let deadline = 1_000_000
    interval.is_entirely_before(self.validity_range, deadline)
  }
}
