- `assets.quantity_of(self.mint, policy_id, royalty_asset_name)` retrieves how many `(500)Royalty` tokens are being minted.
- `assets.restricted_to` + `assets.flatten` ensures that only the single royalty asset name is minted under this policy (no other tokens sneak through).
